---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About Us" 
  description="Discover the story behind Ultraction General Contracting, our values, our mission, and our commitment to transforming spaces with innovation and integrity."
>  
  <div class="fixed inset-0 -z-10 bg-gradient-to-r from-black via-black/80 to-transparent"></div>
  <div class="container mx-auto">
    <section class="hero-section h-screen flex items-center justify-center relative px-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-black/80 via-gray-900 to-black">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <div class="bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_30%_30%,rgba(255,107,53,0.1)_0%,transparent_70%)] absolute inset-0"></div>
        <div class="bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_70%_70%,rgba(255,107,53,0.1)_0%,transparent_70%)] absolute inset-0"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="hero-content text-center z-10 max-w-4xl opacity-0 transform translate-y-12" id="heroContent">
        <h1 class="hero-title font-montserrat text-7xl font-extrabold text-gradient-primary mb-6 leading-tight">
          Our Journey of <br>Excellence
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle text-xl mb-8 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Discover the story behind Ultraction General Contracting, our values, our mission, and our commitment to transforming spaces with innovation and integrity. For over 17 years, we've been building more than structures—we've been building relationships, communities, and a legacy of excellence.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="scroll-indicator absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex flex-col items-center text-gray-400 transition-opacity duration-300 cursor-pointer hover:text-primary">
        <p class="mb-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">Scroll Down</p>
        <div class="scroll-arrow w-8 h-8 border-r-2 border-b-2 border-primary transform rotate-45 animate-arrowBounce"></div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="who-we-are py-24 px-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-black to-black/90 relative">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <div class="bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,rgba(255,107,53,0.05)_0%,transparent_70%)] absolute inset-0"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto relative z-10">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 inline-block relative">
            Who <span class="text-primary">We Are</span>
            <span class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-primary -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full"></span>
          </h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
          <div class="about-image rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
            <img src="/api/placeholder/600/600" alt="About Ultraction" class="w-full h-auto">
          </div>
          
          <div class="about-content">
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 text-gray-300">
              Founded in 2008, Ultraction General Contracting has grown from a small team of skilled craftsmen into a leading construction company known for excellence, innovation, and integrity. Our journey has been defined by a relentless pursuit of quality and a commitment to transforming our clients' visions into reality.
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 text-gray-300">
              Today, we stand as a comprehensive construction services provider with expertise spanning residential, commercial, and infrastructure projects. Our team of over 85 professionals brings specialized knowledge and experience to every project, ensuring exceptional results that exceed expectations.
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
              What sets us apart is our unique blend of traditional craftsmanship and cutting-edge technology. We honor time-tested construction principles while embracing innovative methods and sustainable practices that push the industry forward. This balance allows us to deliver projects that are not only beautiful and functional but also forward-thinking and environmentally responsible.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="director-message py-24 px-6 bg-gradient-to-l from-black to-black/90 relative">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <div class="bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_70%_30%,rgba(255,107,53,0.05)_0%,transparent_70%)] absolute inset-0"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto relative z-10">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 inline-block relative">
            A Message From Our <span class="text-primary">Managing Director</span>
            <span class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-primary -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full"></span>
          </h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="message-container bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-12 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 relative">
          <div class="quote-icon absolute top-8 right-8 text-primary/20 text-8xl font-serif">"</div>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 items-center">
            <div class="director-image col-span-1">
              <div class="rounded-full overflow-hidden w-48 h-48 mx-auto border-4 border-primary/20">
                <img src="/api/placeholder/200/200" alt="Engr. Wael Mamah" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="director-message col-span-2">
              <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 text-gray-300 relative z-10">
                At Ultraction, we believe that construction is about more than just buildings—it's about creating spaces where people live, work, and thrive. Every project we undertake represents an opportunity to positively impact communities and improve lives through thoughtful, quality construction.
              </p>
              
              <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 text-gray-300 relative z-10">
                Our success over the past 17 years stems from our unwavering commitment to three core principles: integrity in all our dealings, excellence in every detail, and innovation in our approach. These values guide every decision we make and every structure we build.
              </p>
              
              <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 text-gray-300 relative z-10">
                As we look to the future, we remain dedicated to pushing boundaries, embracing sustainable practices, and delivering exceptional value to our clients. We're not just building for today—we're creating lasting legacies for generations to come.
              </p>
              
              <div class="director-signature">
                <p class="font-semibold text-xl text-primary">Engr Wael Mamah</p>
                <p class="text-gray-400">Founder & Managing Director</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="vision-mission-section py-24 px-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-black to-black/90 relative">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <div class="bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_30%_70%,rgba(255,107,53,0.05)_0%,transparent_70%)] absolute inset-0"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 max-w-6xl mx-auto relative z-10">
        <div class="vision-card bg-white/5 rounded-2xl p-12 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 transition-all duration-500 hover:transform hover:-translate-y-3 hover:shadow-2xl">
          <div class="vision-icon w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">Our Vision</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
            To be the premier construction company known for transforming architectural visions into exceptional realities, setting new standards for quality, innovation, and client satisfaction in the industry. We aspire to build structures that stand as testaments to excellence, enhancing communities and environments for generations to come.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mission-card bg-white/5 rounded-2xl p-12 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 transition-all duration-500 hover:transform hover:-translate-y-3 hover:shadow-2xl">
          <div class="mission-icon w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
            To deliver exceptional construction services that exceed client expectations through unwavering commitment to quality, integrity, and innovation. We are dedicated to fostering collaborative relationships with clients, architects, and communities, employing sustainable practices, and creating safe, functional, and aesthetically pleasing spaces that enhance the quality of life for all who interact with them.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="values-section py-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-black to-black/90 relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="section-pattern absolute inset-0 opacity-5 pointer-events-none" style="background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width=\"60\" height=\"60\" viewBox=\"0 0 60 60\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"%3E%3Cg fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"%3E%3Cg fill=\"%23b38728\" fill-opacity=\"0.4\"%3E%3Cpath d=\"M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z\"/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E');"></div>
      
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 inline-block relative">
            Our Core <span class="text-primary">Values</span>
            <span class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-primary -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full"></span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto text-gray-300">
            These principles guide every decision we make and every structure we build, forming the foundation of our company culture.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="value-card bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:transform hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-lg">
            <div class="value-icon w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mb-4">Integrity</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
              We conduct business with unwavering honesty, transparency, and ethical standards. Our word is our bond, and we stand behind every project we complete.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="value-card bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:transform hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-lg">
            <div class="value-icon w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mb-4">Excellence</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
              We pursue excellence in every aspect of our work, from the smallest details to the grandest designs. Our commitment to quality is evident in the precision, durability, and beauty of our finished projects.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="value-card bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:transform hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-lg">
            <div class="value-icon w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mb-4">Innovation</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
              We embrace cutting-edge technologies, materials, and methodologies to deliver forward-thinking solutions that address modern challenges while anticipating future needs.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="value-card bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:transform hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-lg">
            <div class="value-icon w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mb-4">Collaboration</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
              We believe in the power of teamwork and partnership. By fostering strong relationships with clients, architects, engineers, and subcontractors, we create synergies that elevate the final result.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="value-card bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:transform hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-lg">
            <div class="value-icon w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h.5A2.5 2.5 0 0020 5.5v-1.65" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mb-4">Sustainability</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
              We are committed to environmentally responsible construction practices that minimize ecological impact while maximizing resource efficiency and creating healthier spaces for occupants.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="value-card bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:transform hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-lg">
            <div class="value-icon w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v13m0-13V6a2 2 0 112 2h-2zm0 0V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 109.5 8H12zm-7 4h14M5 12a2 2 0 110-4h14a2 2 0 110 4M5 12v7a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-7" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mb-4">Client-Centric</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
              Our clients' vision, needs, and satisfaction are at the heart of everything we do. We listen attentively, communicate clearly, and work tirelessly to exceed expectations at every stage of the project.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="timeline-section relative py-32 overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-r from-black to-black/90">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <div class="bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_70%_70%,rgba(255,107,53,0.05)_0%,transparent_70%)] absolute inset-0"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="timeline-header text-center mb-24 relative z-10">
        <h2 class="section-title font-montserrat text-5xl font-bold text-gradient-primary mb-6 relative inline-block">
          Our Evolution
          <span class="absolute w-3/5 h-1 bg-gradient-primary bottom-[-10px] left-[20%] rounded-sm"></span>
        </h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          From humble beginnings to industry leadership, our timeline showcases the key milestones that have shaped Ultraction's growth and success over the past 17 years.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="timeline w-4/5 max-w-6xl mx-auto relative px-5 z-10">
        <div class="timeline-line absolute top-0 left-1/2 w-0.5 h-full bg-gradient-primary -translate-x-1/2"></div>
        
        <div class="timeline-item relative w-1/2 opacity-0 transform translate-y-12 transition-all duration-600 mb-16 left-0 text-right pr-16" data-year="2008">
          <div class="timeline-content bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-xl backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 transition-transform duration-300 hover:transform hover:-translate-y-3 hover:shadow-2xl">
            <span class="timeline-year inline-block font-montserrat text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4 px-5 py-2 bg-primary/10 rounded-full">2008</span>
            <h3 class="timeline-title text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">Foundation</h3>
            <p class="timeline-text text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
              Ultraction began as a small team of skilled craftsmen dedicated to quality workmanship and exceptional client satisfaction. Founded by John Ultraction, a master builder with over 20 years of experience, the company initially focused on residential renovations and small commercial projects. Our founding principles of integrity, quality, and innovation continue to guide us today.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="timeline-item relative w-1/2 opacity-0 transform translate-y-12 transition-all duration-600 mb-16 left-1/2 pl-16" data-year="2012">
          <div class="timeline-content bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-xl backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 transition-transform duration-300 hover:transform hover:-translate-y-3 hover:shadow-2xl">
            <span class="timeline-year inline-block font-montserrat text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4 px-5 py-2 bg-primary/10 rounded-full">2012</span>
            <h3 class="timeline-title text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">First Major Project</h3>
            <p class="timeline-text text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
              Secured our first multi-million dollar contract to build the Oakridge Community Center, a 45,000 sq ft facility that showcased our ability to handle complex, large-scale projects. This milestone project earned us recognition for innovative design implementation and on-time delivery, establishing our reputation for excellence in the commercial sector.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="timeline-item relative w-1/2 opacity-0 transform translate-y-12 transition-all duration-600 mb-16 left-0 text-right pr-16" data-year="2015">
          <div class="timeline-content bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-xl backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 transition-transform duration-300 hover:transform hover:-translate-y-3 hover:shadow-2xl">
            <span class="timeline-year inline-block font-montserrat text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4 px-5 py-2 bg-primary/10 rounded-full">2015</span>
            <h3 class="timeline-title text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">Major Expansion</h3>
            <p class="timeline-text text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
              We evolved into a full-service general contracting firm, expanding our capabilities to tackle diverse projects across residential, commercial, and industrial sectors. Our team grew to include specialized experts in every construction discipline, from structural engineers to interior design specialists. This strategic expansion allowed us to offer comprehensive, end-to-end construction solutions while maintaining our commitment to quality and personalized service.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="timeline-item relative w-1/2 opacity-0 transform translate-y-12 transition-all duration-600 mb-16 left-1/2 pl-16" data-year="2018">
          <div class="timeline-content bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-xl backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 transition-transform duration-300 hover:transform hover:-translate-y-3 hover:shadow-2xl">
            <span class="timeline-year inline-block font-montserrat text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4 px-5 py-2 bg-primary/10 rounded-full">2018</span>
            <h3 class="timeline-title text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">Digital Transformation</h3>
            <p class="timeline-text text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
              Implemented cutting-edge Building Information Modeling (BIM) technology and digital project management systems, revolutionizing our approach to construction planning and execution. This digital transformation enhanced our ability to visualize projects before breaking ground, identify potential issues early, and streamline collaboration between all stakeholders, resulting in greater efficiency and precision.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="timeline-item relative w-1/2 opacity-0 transform translate-y-12 transition-all duration-600 mb-16 left-0 text-right pr-16" data-year="2020">
          <div class="timeline-content bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-xl backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 transition-transform duration-300 hover:transform hover:-translate-y-3 hover:shadow-2xl">
            <span class="timeline-year inline-block font-montserrat text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4 px-5 py-2 bg-primary/10 rounded-full">2020</span>
            <h3 class="timeline-title text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">Sustainability Focus</h3>
            <p class="timeline-text text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
              Embracing eco-friendly construction practices became our priority, earning multiple LEED certifications and industry recognition for our green building initiatives. We pioneered new approaches to sustainable construction in our region, including the development of our proprietary "EcoFrame" building system that reduces material waste by 40% while improving energy efficiency. Our Riverfront Eco-Office project became a case study in sustainable commercial construction, winning the Green Building Excellence Award.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="timeline-item relative w-1/2 opacity-0 transform translate-y-12 transition-all duration-600 mb-16 left-1/2 pl-16" data-year="2025">
          <div class="timeline-content bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-xl backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 transition-transform duration-300 hover:transform hover:-translate-y-3 hover:shadow-2xl">
            <span class="timeline-year inline-block font-montserrat text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4 px-5 py-2 bg-primary/10 rounded-full">2025</span>
            <h3 class="timeline-title text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white">Industry Leadership</h3>
            <p class="timeline-text text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
              Today, Ultraction stands as a leader in innovative construction solutions, having completed over 200 successful projects valued at more than $1.5 billion. Our commitment to cutting-edge techniques, digital construction technologies, and exceptional client service defines our reputation. We've established the Ultraction Innovation Lab, a research facility dedicated to advancing construction methodologies and materials science, and launched our mentorship program to develop the next generation of construction professionals.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
